      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Summary, etc.</strong> <div class="description">Text of the summary, abstract, review, etc. When no distinction between levels of
                              detail in the text is required, subfield $a contains all the text. When
                              a distinction is appropriate, subfield $a contains a brief statement,
                              with additional information being provided in subfield $b.
         </div>
         <div class="example">
