      <div class="subfield"><strong>$u - Uniform Resource Identifier</strong> <div class="description">Uniform Resource Identifier (URI), for example a URL or URN, which provides
                              electronic access data in a standard syntax. This data can be used for automated
                              access to an electronic item using one of the Internet protocols.
         </div>
