         <div class="subfield"><strong>$2 - Source</strong> <div class="description">Source code for the particular classification system used (for example, the MPAA
                                 (USA) and BBFC (UK) film classification systems) to construct the content advice
                                 statement recorded in subfield $a. Code from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/standards/sourcelist/content-advice.html">Content Advice Classification Source Codes </a></em>.
            </div>
            <div class="example">
               <table width="100%">
