      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation</strong> -  This field ends with a period unless another mark of punctuation is present. If the
                     final subfield is subfield $u, the mark of punctuation precedes that
                     subfield.
      </div>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Display Constants</strong> - Introductory terms such as <em>Summary:</em> or <em>Subject:</em> are not carried in the
                     MARC record. They may be system generated as display constants associated with the first
                     indicator value.
